{
  "texts": [
    "The use of chat bots includes but not limited to disease identification via image analysis, retail, media, and general inquiries related to agronomic practices (Talaviya et al., 2020; Momaya et al., 2021; Ong et al., 2021; Chandolikar et al., 2022).",
    "This could speed up the management process on farmers' end.",
    "For instance, identification of an infection could help farmers with the timely use of perspective insecticide.",
    "However, the chat bots are prone to errors and sometimes could produce inaccurate results of queries.",
    "Therefore, further training of ML models is needed."
  ]
}